cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "Information-Theoretic Unification (ITU) Tier 0 v3.0: Intermediate Integration of Tier 1 #1-#16 — 16-Vertex Polytope, Meta-Axioms, 160 Falsifiable Predictions, and Pass-2 Framework"
message: "If you use this work, please cite it as below."
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: Terada
    given-names: Munehiro
    affiliation: Roboken
    email: munehiro.terada@roboken2.com
abstract: >
  Tier 0 v3.0 of the Information-Theoretic Unification (ITU)
  programme (Terada 2026, concept DOI 10.5281/zenodo.20109209;
  previous version v2.0.0 at 10.5281/zenodo.20133709). v3.0 is
  the Pass-1 intermediate integration covering the 16 Tier 1
  papers completed in Phase 43-106 (the 50% Pass-1 milestone,
  110 of 220 planned phases).
  Phase 107 establishes motivation and the 24-chapter v3.0 plan.
  Phase 108 develops the graph theory of the ITU polytope: 16
  vertices, 60 edges, average degree 7.5, power-law exponent
  gamma=0.79. Top hub Smart Cities #16 with degree 15 (URBAN
  ULTIMATE HUB). Super-hubs Climate #11 and Communications #14
  tied at degree 11. Spectral clustering yields 3 communities:
  engineering / life-society / climate-cosmos. Five meta-axioms
  beta-1 (cross-cutting K-flow), beta-2 (hub property), beta-3
  (conservation), beta-4 (emergence), beta-5 (symmetry breaking).
  Phase 109 aggregates 160 falsifiable predictions (16 Tier 1 ×
  10), grand P_avg = 0.59. Top 50 selected by Score = Importance
  × Probability × Verifiability. Falsifiability audit: 50% Strong,
  31% Medium, 19% Weak. Pass-2 priority Tier 1 for Phase 221-230:
  #1 QC, #2 AI/ASI, #5 Cancer, #10 Energy, #11 Climate, #16 Smart
  Cities, #13 Robotics, #14 Comm, #4 Semi, #7 Psychiatry. 4-stage
  translation framework (development / PoC / commercialization /
  diffusion).
  Phase 110 closes v3.0 with the five-block classification of
  Tier 1 #1-#16 (Engineering Pentagon + Medicine Triangle +
  Social-Humanities + Climate-Cosmos + Industry-Urban) and the
  Block A roadmap (Tier 1 #17-#25, Phase 111-180): Quantum
  Gravity, Black Holes, Cosmology, Standard Model, Statistical
  Mechanics, Mathematics, Information Theory, Complexity Theory,
  Foundations of Physics. Evolution axis: v3.0 (Phase 110, 16
  Tier 1) → v4.0 (Phase 220, 45 Tier 1, Pass-1 final) → v5.0
  (Phase 250, Pass-2 final).
  Central thesis: Tier 0 v3.0 captures the ITU programme at its
  halfway point. The 16-vertex polytope is the structural
  snapshot, the meta-axioms beta-1〜beta-5 are the dynamical
  layer, and the 160 falsifiable predictions form the empirical
  bridge to Pass-2. Pass-1 interpretive synthesis; numerical
  results aggregate and re-organize prior Tier 1 outputs. No
  new physical predictions beyond what each Tier 1 paper
  already contains. The polytope graph, meta-axioms, and Pass-2
  priority list are organizational scaffolding for the next 110
  phases (111-220).
keywords:
  - Information theory
  - Quantum information
  - Modular Hamiltonian
  - Entanglement entropy
  - Network science
  - Scale-free networks
  - Complex systems
  - Falsifiability
  - Unified theory
  - Interdisciplinary research
